A comprehensive and essential course on Big Data and the most innovative/affirmed technology.There is a kind of small problem with the peer reviews, that make the end of the course difficult at times to accomplish, stimulating a mechanism of graduate exchange in the forums, because of the lack of people that can evaluate others immediately.Finally, the tool used for the graduate assignment is available for free only for 14 days and the assignment itself is not so clear to understand.For this reasons, i gave three stars only, even if the course quality and the material is very good, the assignment could be improved a lot and is decreasing my final evaluation.
